And come to think of it...<br>
If you drop all the vast wasted mass for the pusher, bombs, loaders, ejectors, shocksystem, with all the array of complex moving parts, ran your reactors with the percentage of nuclear fuel equal to that amount that actually transfers energy to the pusher (and not lost in space), I wouldn't be surprised if you achieve ~greater~ performance with some type of particle accelerator engine that won't be illegal.<br>
<br>
